title: Authority to plan, improve, develop, operate, and maintain industrial parks
context: [ยง171-133] Authority to plan, improve, develop, operate, and maintain industrial parks. The board shall plan, improve, develop, operate, and maintain each industrial park designated pursuant to section 171-132. The planning, improving, developing, operation, and maintenance of an industrial park shall be in accordance with this chapter. [L 1988, c 361, pt of ยง1]
